    "title": "Uwepo wa Roho Mtakatifu",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "uwepo wa roho mtakatifu",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kitabu cha Matendo kinasisitiza uwepo na nguvu za Roho Mtakatifu. Kabla ya Roho kuja, Yesu alizungumza kuhusu ushawishi wa Roho kwa wafuasi wake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">1:8</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15-John14:17\">Yohana 14:15–17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7-John16:15\">16:7–15</a>). Roho aliwaongoza waziwazi kanisa la mwanzo katika kuchagua viongozi waliojaa Roho ili kushughulikia mahitaji ya wajane wa Kiyunani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1-Acts6:7\">Matendo 6:1–7</a>). Hawa walikuwa wajane wa Kiyahudi wanaozungumza Kiyunani ambao walihitaji msaada katika ugawaji wa chakula wa kila siku. Roho Mtakatifu aliwachagua mitume Barnaba na Sauli kwa kazi ya umishonari (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1-Acts13:5\">13:1–5</a>). Wakati baraza la kwanza la kanisa lilipokutana kujadili uanachama wa watu wasio Wayahudi (mataifa), walifuata mwelekeo wa Roho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">15:28</a>).</p><p>Roho Mtakatifu aliwajaza wafanyakazi Wakristo Stefano na Filipo kuhubiri kwa nguvu za Roho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1-Acts8:40\">Matendo 6:1–8:40</a>). Roho alitia nguvu huduma ya mtume Paulo tangu mwanzo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:17\">9:17</a>). Katika kitabu cha Matendo, kanisa liliongezeka na kupanuka chini ya mwongozo na nguvu za Roho Mtakatifu (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:41-Acts2:47\">41–47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:32\">5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:15\">8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:17\">17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">9:31</a>). Kwa sababu ya jukumu muhimu la Roho katika Matendo, watu mara nyingi huliita “Matendo ya Roho Mtakatifu.”</p><p>Roho Mtakatifu hufanya kazi kwa njia mbalimbali:</p><ul><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu anatoa na kurejesha uhai (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">Mwanzo 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:24-Ps104:30\">Zaburi 104:24–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1-Ezek37:14\">Ezekieli 37:1–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:32\">Yoeli 2:28–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9-Rom8:11\">Warumi 8:9–11</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu anaita na kuchagua wafanyakazi kwa ajili ya huduma ya Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">Matendo 13:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">20:28</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu huwaongoza watumishi wa Mungu mahali na wakati anapotaka watende (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">Matendo 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:15\">9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19-Acts10:20\">10:19–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:12\">11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6\">16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:13\">1 Wakorintho 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:12\">1 Petro 1:12</a>). </p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu aliongoza uandishi wa Maandiko (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2 Timotheo 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:20-2Pet1:21\">2 Petro 1:20–21</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu hufundisha kanisa kuhusu ujumbe wa Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">Yohana 14:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1 Wakorintho 12:3</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu huonyesha nguvu ya habari njema kuhusu Yesu (injili) kupitia ishara na maajabu ya miujiza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">Matendo 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">Waebrania 2:4</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu huwafundisha watu wa Mungu ukweli wa Maandiko (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:16\">Matendo 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:8\">Waebrania 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:15-Heb10:17\">10:15–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:11-1Pet1:12\">1 Petro 1:11–12</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu anashuhudia kuhusu Yesu na kumletea utukufu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">Yohana 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:14\">16:13–14</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu huwafanya watu kutambua dhambi zao na hitaji lao la habari njema (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">Yohana 16:8</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu anawaonya dhidi ya ukaidi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:11\">Waebrania 3:7–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:15\">15</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu huwapa watu wa Mungu vipawa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:4-1Cor12:11\">1 Wakorintho 12:4–11</a>).</p></li><li><p>Roho Mtakatifu huwapa nguvu kushiriki habari njema, kumtumikia Bwana, na kufanya kazi kwa ajili ya Ufalme wa Mungu.</p></li></ul><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15-John14:17\">Yohana 14:15–17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7-John16:15\">16:7–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">Matendo 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:16\">16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:41-Acts2:47\">41–47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:32\">5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:1-Acts6:7\">6:1–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:15\">8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:17\">17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:15\">9:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:17\">17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19-Acts10:20\">10:19–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:12\">11:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1-Acts13:5\">13:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">15:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6\">16:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:13\">1 Wakorintho 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:1-1Cor12:11\">12:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">Waefeso 1:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2 Timotheo 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">Waebrania 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7-Heb3:11\">3:7–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:15\">15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:8\">9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:15-Heb10:17\">10:15–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:11-1Pet1:12\">1 Petro 1:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:20-2Pet1:21\">2 Petro 1:20–21</a></p>",
